{
  "doc_id": "51516",
  "text": "Genes were identified using Prodigal [CITATION_1] as part of the DOE-JGI genome annotation pipeline [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] , following by a round of manual curation using the JGI GenePRIMP pipeline [CITATION_4] . The predicted CDSs were translated and searched against the Integrated Microbial Genomes (IMG) non-redundant database, UniProt, TIGERFam, Pfam, PRIAM, KEGG, COG, and InterPro databases. These data sources were combined to assert a product description for each predicted protein. Additional gene prediction analysis and functional annotation was performed within the Integrated Microbial GenomesExpert Review (IMG-ER) platform [CITATION_5] .",
